Text: no subjectto Sienna Plantation to the Sam Houston tollway south go south Stay on the Sam Houston tollway past Hwy and exit South Main Hwy and turn right to Murphy Road Turn left onto Murphy Road and stay on Murphy Road until you get to Hwy and then turn left Take Hwy to Sienna Parkway and turn right onto Sienna Parkway Go approximately three miles and after you go over the railroad tracks turn right onto Sienna Trace You will see the courts after you turn onto Sienna Trace The early lines start at and it will take at least hour to get there so anyone interested in leaving from the club should meet at please Beth is the only person playing at but I am staying until she is finished so anyone wishing to stay can catch a ride home Lisa
